Type: Package
Package: GRM
Title: Comprehensive Graded Response Model Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("First", "Last", , "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Avi Kluger
Maintainer: Avi Kluger <avikluger@gmail.com>
Description: A comprehensive wrapper for conducting Graded Response Model
    (GRM) analysis using Item Response Theory. Provides streamlined
    workflow for psychometric analysis of polytomous items with automated
    reporting, visualization, and best items identification. Supports both
    unidimensional and multidimensional models with enhanced diagnostics.
License: GPL (>= 3)
URL: https://github.com/avi-kluger/GRM
